 # System Architecture[m
 [m
 ## Components[m
[31m-- Mobile web client (React + Tailwind)[m
[31m-- Messaging (SMS via Twilio, 10DLC compliant)[m
[31m-- Identity (passkeys/WebAuthn, optional OTP assist)[m
[31m-- Non-custodial Hedera wallets (Ed25519)[m
[31m-- HCS10 topics for append-only events (hashinals)[m
[31m-- Indexer service (stateless validators + Merkle checkpointing)[m
[31m-- Optional Trust Slot Registry contract (later hardening)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Frontend:** React + Tailwind mobile web[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Identity/Keys:** **Magic.link** (passkeys/WebAuthn) for key management & recovery (DeRec post-MVP)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Messaging:** **XMTP SDK** (wallet/alias chat; E2E). **SMS only** for invites/claims. HCS10 for campaign/system triggers.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Payments:** **TRST stablecoin** via **Brale** (KYC/AML + custody/compliance) with **MatterFi SDK**; **KNS** Send-to-Name; QR-pay[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Engagement:** Hedera **NFTs** (redeemable/POAP-style) + **hashinals** (portable reputation artifacts)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Commitment Layer:** **Circle of Trust Registry** (contract) enforcing **9 device-bound tokens (DBTs)** per user, quiet unbonding & per-slot cooldowns[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Contacts Layer:** Unlimited, consented contact graph (private by default; low weight)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Indexer:** Stateless validators + deterministic reducer + **hourly Merkle checkpoint** to a dedicated HCS topic[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Secrets & Privacy:** Cohort-peppered HMAC IDs derived in **KMS/HSM**; pepper versioning & rotation[m
 [m
[31m-## Diagrams[m
[31m-See `/assets/diagrams/` and keep SVG source committed.[m
[32m+[m[32m## Data Flows[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Commitment:** COMMIT ? (UNBOND) ? REVOKE; registry updates bitmap; indexer reduces to edges; hourly checkpoint[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Contacts:** CONTACT_ADD/REMOVE; indexer maintains private graph; opt-in sharing[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Messaging:** XMTP consent/block/report + rate limits; HCS triggers; SMS invites only[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Payments:** TRST transfers via Brale/MatterFi; KNS resolution; policy **pay trusted first**[m
