[32m+[m[32mThis repository is the **authoritative source** for the TrustMesh product vision, architecture, UX, compliance, and deployment model ï¿½ built on the Scend Context Engineering kernel.[m
 [m
[32m+[m[32m## Core Mandate[m
[32m+[m[32mTrustMesh is a **Hedera-first**, privacy-preserving trust graph that turns IRL trusted relationships into **cryptographically verifiable commitments**.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mEvery deployment must implement the **three context loops** in this order:[m
[32m+[m[32mNOTE: Context Loops are sequential in activation (Messaging must be live before Payments, before Engagement) ï¿½ this matches the operating philosophy in CONTEXT_ENGINNERING.md[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. **Messaging** ï¿½ **XMTP-powered** threads by wallet or alias. *XMTP is not SMS.* SMS is used only for **invites/claims**; all chat occurs over XMTP. HCS10 emits system/campaign triggers.[m
[32m+[m[32m2. **Payments** ï¿½ **TRST stablecoin** via **Brale** (KYC/AML + custody/compliance) with **MatterFi SDK** for flows. Wallets auto-provisioned; **Send-to-Name (KNS)** and QR-pay supported.[m
[32m+[m[32m3. **Engagement** ï¿½ Hedera **NFT/hashinal** rewards and **Circle of Trust** allocations (9 **device-bound** commitment slots per user, quiet unbonding, immutable acceptance).[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Non-Negotiables[m
[32m+[m[32m- **TRST is the only payment rail** for stablecoin flows in MVP (**Brale handles KYC/AML**).[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Circle of Trust** governs strong trust: **9 device-bound tokens (DBTs)** per user; revocable with quiet unbonding and per-slot cooldowns.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Contacts (lite trust) are included**: unlimited, consented connections for discovery/routing; low weight; private by default.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Hedera-first**: HTS for assets, HCS10 for events, hashinals for portable reputation.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Licensed kernel** ï¿½ not public open source. Cloning/deployments require contractual authorization.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Repository Structure[m
[32m+[m[32m- **1_overview/** ï¿½ Vision, positioning, Circle of Trust principles[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **2_architecture/** ï¿½ Hedera-based system design, protocol, specs[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **3_ux_workflows/** ï¿½ Loop-driven UX (Messaging ? Payments ? Engagement)[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **4_research_academic/** ï¿½ Research alignment, IRB-ready privacy posture[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **5_development_plan/** ï¿½ MVP scope, sprints, risks, deployment[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **6_legal_compliance/** ï¿½ GDPR, CCPA, TCPA, data retention[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **7_collaboration_governance/** ï¿½ Contribution guidelines, glossary, style[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m- **assets/** ï¿½ Diagrams, wireframes, visuals[m[41m  [m
